{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"format-number","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/format-number","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>format-number</code>関数は数値を評価し、与えられた形式の数値を表す文字列を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">format-number(<em>number</em> ,<em>pattern</em> [,<em>decimal-format</em>] )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"number\"><code><em>number</em></code></dt>\n <dd>フォーマットする数値</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"pattern\"><code><em>pattern</em></code></dt>\n <dd>JDK 1.1 DecimalFormatクラスの形式の文字列。（<a href=\"https://java.sun.com/products/archive/jdk/1.1/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">JDK 1.1</a>のドキュメントはオンラインでは入手できません。<a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/jp/6/api/java/text/DecimalFormat.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Java SE 6 DecimalFormat</a>はこちらです）</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"decimal-format\"><code><em>decimal-format</em></code> (任意)</dt>\n <dd>使用する数値書式を定義する<code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/decimal-format\">xsl:decimal-format</a></code>要素の名前。省略すると、デフォルトの10進形式が使用されます。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>新しい形式の数値を表す文字列。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注記","isH3":true,"content":"<p>この関数はXPathへのXSLT固有の追加です。コアXPath関数ライブラリの一部ではありません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xslt#function-format-number\" rel=\" noopener\">XSLT 1.0 12.3</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko のサポート","isH3":true,"content":"<p>サポート済み</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"format-number関数は数値を評価し、与えられた形式の数値を表す文字列を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"format-number","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"format-number","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"format-number","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"format-number","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xpath/functions/format-number","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/xpath/functions/format-number/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/format-number","title":"format-number"}],"pageTitle":"format-number - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}